author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: "Life is a funny thing. We only get so many years to live it, so we have to do everything we can to make sure those years are as full as they can be. We shouldn't waste time on things that might happen someday, or maybe even never." - Colleen Hoover

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text:
"Sometimes life doesn’t give you what you want, not because you don’t deserve it, but because you deserve so much more."
Amna.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Your only permanent home is your body. Take care of it.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Disappear. Grow in private. No distractions. Full focus.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: You can't beat a person who never gives up.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Forgiving people in silence and never speaking to them again is a form of self care.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: It’s going to be hard, but hard does not mean impossible.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: “I will push you from the east of suffering to the west of peace.”

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Do more than just talk, act. Do more than just promise, deliver." - Steve Maraboli

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Be low key. Be private. Be humble.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text:
"If you want to be successful, you must respect one rule – Never lie to yourself."

- Paulo Coelho

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text:
"I smile because I have survived everything the world has thrown at me. I smile because when I was knocked down I got back up."
Amna.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Removing yourself from situations where you don’t feel valued is  self-care.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: "Don't compare your Chapter 1 to someone else's Chapter 20."

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Normalize removing yourself from anywhere you feel weird vibes, negative energy or sneaky shit.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Better to be king of your silence than slave of your words.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: I will remember you, but as lesson.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: You cannot avoid pain, but you can chose to overcome it. — Paul Coelho

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: It’s not how big the house is,  it’s how happy the home is.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Always pray to have eyes that see the best, a heart that forgives the worst, a mind that forgets the bad, and a soul that never loses faith.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text: Be someone's sunshine when their skies are grey.

author: Amna Sher Ali Shaker
text:
“when you succeed be humble.”

-imam Ali (a.s)
